name: ceci n'est pas un maïs
description:
HAND DRAWN t shirts. Original Designs. T shirts are made one at a time, by me... so each will look slightly different! For more pictures and different examples email me at whereiscalla@gmail.com
In the case of this t shirt, I use real life corn models, old, new, genetically modified or "organic" (if there still such thing), or what's left of them in my head...
The concept is a tribute to Magritte, and a wake up call of WHAT IS OUR FOOD? the phrase Ceci n'est pas un maïs, can also be translated into any language, for now I have done it in english, spanish and french...

AVAILABLE IN ALL SIZES, V necks or Round necks. White.

name: Wake up people (ants)
description:
HAND DRAWN t shirts. Original Designs. T shirts are made one at a time, so each will look slightly different!
With this t shirt i sometimes change the position of the world and the position of the fish going trough space! You can get it as you see it in the picture or ask to see more pictures! whereiscalla@gmail.com

This t shirt is also a wake up call, for all the people of the world, coming from a flying fish, who wasn´t supposed to fly, but is now so we can open our eyes to the things that are happening and DO Something, get off the line and open you mind!

AVAILABLE IN ALL SIZES, V necks or Round necks.
T shirts are Ives Saint Laurein, (so far) WHITE. (for double xx t shirts will be a different brand but same style)
